g.text: Vietnam released an estimated 525 MtCO2e in 2023 (excl. LULUCF), a change of +10.7 % compared to the previous year. Per
capita GHG emissions were 5.3 tCO2e in 2023. Cumulative CO2 emissions since 1850 were 14.1 GtCO2, or about 1% of global
emissions to date. Sources: EDGAR v9, GCB 2023, UNFCCC, Grassi et al. 2021
